ProtoResult:
. "If $\mathbf{X}$ and $\mathbf{Y}$ are any two vectors in 
   $\R^n$ then \begin{equation} |\mathbf{X}\cdot\mathbf{Y}|\le 
   |\mathbf{X}|\,|\mathbf{Y}|, \end{equation} with equality if 
   and only if one of the vectors is a scalar multiple of the 
   other."
